reviews.review_text: i was at this show! it was amazing! the boys were on fire!!shakedown,help,slip,franklin were out of this world!!!baby blue topped off the night!!! long drive back from jersey to va!!

blew me away I was at this run of shows, and holy toledo i was blown away. This was my first time seeing Branford with the band. Jerry actually looked like he was having fun.I'LL ride a mailtrain baby.....
